H. S. GRAY et al. v. Myrta BLIGHT, Administratrix. No. 2021. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. June 28, 1940. Earl W. Wilson, of Denver, Colo., for appellants. W. A. Alexander, of Denver, Colo., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS and LEWIS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed, at costs of appellants, for the reason that the order appealed from is not a final appealable order.
